Life table for the US in 2015

Source: R/data_all_cause_mortality.R
all_cause_mortality.Rd

A dataset with all-cause mortality rates from US 2015 life table estimates

all_cause_mortality

Format

A data frame with 11 rows and 5 variables:

Year

calendar year

Age

age, in years

Female

mortality rate for females

Male

mortality rate for males

Total

mortality rate for the total population
